snippet.title: JFreeChart
snippet.description: JFreeChart is a free (LGPL) chart library for the Java(tm) platform. It supports bar charts, pie charts, line charts, time series charts, scatter plots, histograms, simple Gantt charts, Pareto charts, bubble plots, dials, thermometers and more.

snippet.title: SAGE - SCADA Animation Graphic Editor
snippet.description: SAGE is an add-on feature for Inkscape to enable real-time mimic graphic animation in SVG running with IntegraXor SCADA animation engine. Animation effects incorporated such as "Bar", "Color", "Rotate", "Opacity", "Zoom", "Slider", etc.

snippet.title: KeePass Favicon Downloader
snippet.description: A KeePass plugin that downloads and stores favicons. A favicon is the little icon / logo used to identify many websites, typically displayed in the browser's address bar, bookmark list and on tabs.

snippet.title: CCMenu
snippet.description: Displays the status of continuous integration servers in the Mac OS X menu bar. Works with all recent versions of CruiseControl and all servers that support "cctray" feeds, which includes ThoughtWorks Go, Jenkins, Hudson, and others.
